webkit2png is a command line tool that creates png screenshots of webpages.

This version is ment to be a drop in replacement for CutyCapt.

Want to help ? Fork it on github and send me a pull request!
https://github.com/bjornblomqvist/webkit2png

For original version visit http://www.paulhammond.org/webkit2png/

-- Plans
  
  - Mutable urls
  - Daemon mode to remove the startup delay